title: UNDERCOVER: Beto O'Rourke's Pathetic Town Hall | Louder With Crowder
description: We sent a team undercover to infiltrate a Beto O'Rourke campaign rally, and what we found was shocking. After Beto used 19 dead children for a cheap political stunt, today is the perfect time to release it! We're also going deep into the Sussmam trial. SPOILER: Everything Trump said was right! #Beto #Uvadale #GregAbbott
